I"9<p>Include function is one of the most common function. It is used to include files which contain code which are repeatedly used e.g footers, headers e.t.c.</p>

<p>In php, there are 4 ways to include a file,</p>

<ul>
  <li>include</li>
  <li>include_once</li>
  <li>required</li>
  <li>required_once</li>
</ul>
